Class ServerThreadPoolManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • suncertify.nw.ServerThreadPoolManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerService

    public class ServerThreadPoolManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServerService
    This class represents the server thread pool manager. The pool manager keeps track of available server threads and adds new threads to the pool when necessary.
